The '''heavy combat suit''' was a type of [[Armor/Legends|armor]] that offered more protection than the basic model of [[combat suit]]. The heavy combat suit was heavier overall than other combat suits, and not quite as flexible, but many considered the trade-offs worthwhile. It was a good source of defense from physical attacks and light blaster fire.

Heavy combat suits were in use during the [[Jedi Civil War]] and the [[Dark Wars]] that followed it.

